column2: "Heeey! Bravers here! Don't support those Bouncers, go Braver!!"
"Come on, Io. Say something too!"
"...I don't think there's anyone out here to hear us..."
"Satisfaction lies in the effort, not in the attainment! Full effort is full victory!"
"If you say so... but why drag me along?"
"Uwa-! S-sir! Is that you?"
"What are we doing, you say? Raising Braver appeal of course! Who better to promote than the founder?"
"I mean, have you seen those Bouncer administrators? Their class was practically just approved and they're everywhere."
"We can't afford to lose to them! We've got to let the world know what it means to be a Braver!"
"And that explains why the lovely Io is here to help the cause!"
"Help... against my will you mean..."
"Now that's not very nice. I invited you in on the action because you looked lonely."
"You didn't say anything about this publicity campaign... too late now."
"Well, the point is that you're here now. You're so kind, Io."
"I-I am not! Don't say things like that!"
"1. She's got a point..."
"2. You're so sweet, Io."
"S-sir!! Not you too!?"
"Oh? Is that blush I see? You little cutie pie!"
"E-everyone just shut up! Excuse me, Sir!"
"I might have overdid it a tad... Catch you later!"
